div.p:
Because of the variety of our controls on East-West trade, we have a number of
                    fields in which we can take action: 

—a decrease in the differentiation between the U.S. export controls
                            and those of other Western countries;

—a decrease in the level of the international controls;

—credits for the Soviet Union;

—a decrease in our discrimination against imports from the European
                            Communist countries.
